Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:40.47,main,,0,0,0,,Night has fallen since I was separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:48.18,main,,0,0,0,,Darn! I shouldn't have gone hunting this deep into the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:51.28,main,,0,0,0,,There's even rumors that monsters lurk around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.05,main,,0,0,0,,Sound of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:59.58,main,,0,0,0,,Signs of life! I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:14.77,main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.94,main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's why you're become lost? You must be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:28.90,main,,0,0,0,,My home's nothing but a shack, but please rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.37,main,,0,0,0,,Right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.08,0:01:35.58,main,,0,0,0,,You're living by yourself this deep in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:39.23,main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I live here by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:42.54,main,,0,0,0,,You're not inconvenienced from the lack of foodstuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.73,main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.68,main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see, she does seem well nourished...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.98,main,,0,0,0,,There's not much I can do for hospitality, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:57.06,main,,0,0,0,,Hospitality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.31,main,,0,0,0,,If it's hospitality you're offering, then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:04.23,main,,0,0,0,,You're asking for it, living by yourself and inviting me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:08.24,main,,0,0,0,,P-Please, please do not put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:17.68,main,,0,0,0,,What a delicious looking body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.97,main,,0,0,0,,How cute! Don't worry, I'll treat you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.96,main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind you living in my mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.57,main,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.82,main,,0,0,0,,Why? You'll be able to live comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:38.79,main,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.29,main,,0,0,0,,That because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:44.11,main,,0,0,0,,Today's going to be the last time we meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.30,main,,0,0,0,,What the-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.00,main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm trapped-!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.73,main,,0,0,0,,The time is the Heian period.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:10.24,main,,0,0,0,,During this age, whether it was in the mountains or populated towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:12.68,main,,0,0,0,,monsters were running rampant on the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.77,main,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.22,main,,0,0,0,,Kiyomori-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.19,main,,0,0,0,,Both of you, sisters. Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.99,main,,0,0,0,,Wealth and power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.52,main,,0,0,0,,I'm the envy of the surrounding provinces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.52,main,,0,0,0,,I have all you can imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:47.34,main,,0,0,0,,All this power, isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.42,main,,0,0,0,,It is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:57.40,main,,0,0,0,,Crush all that oppose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.19,main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:11.45,main,,0,0,0,,Shaga-nee, you're going to get involved with the humans again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.62,main,,0,0,0,,Oh it's you, Ayame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.57,main,,0,0,0,,Things gets boring, living 330 years in the same forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:20.57,main,,0,0,0,,I see, you sure like humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.83,main,,0,0,0,,Those are the Kamuro hounds of the House of Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:28.09,main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that kid did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.55,main,,0,0,0,,Shaga-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.15,main,,0,0,0,,That's a monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.77,main,,0,0,0,,She changed to a humanoid form...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.75,main,,0,0,0,,More seem to be on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.75,main,,0,0,0,,Where were you wanting go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.20,main,,0,0,0,,You're from Kurama Temple, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.34,main,,0,0,0,,Go back before it gets dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.08,main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:10.43,main,,0,0,0,,I just saved your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.97,main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I needed help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.69,main,,0,0,0,,I was able to fight them myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.15,main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.16,main,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.98,main,,0,0,0,,Where did you want to go? I'll carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.62,main,,0,0,0,,Let me go! I'll get there with my own two feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.46,main,,0,0,0,,You want to be dropped off right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.44,main,,0,0,0,,Then... Ichijou...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.45,main,,0,0,0,,I want to go to Ichijou. Mother's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.18,main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.84,main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:57.15,main,,0,0,0,,Ushiwaka... Is it really you, Ushiwaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.00,main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.50,main,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.73,main,,0,0,0,,Ushiwaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:12.73,main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very for saving him from danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:17.07,main,,0,0,0,,This boy is Ushiwaka, an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.19,main,,0,0,0,,He's kept under surveillance by the House of Taira
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.67,main,,0,0,0,,and unless he becomes a monk, the poor boy's life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:29.35,main,,0,0,0,,There is something I wish to ask of you, traveling monk Shaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:36.02,main,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to protect Ushiwaka and get him to the safe lands of Ooshu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.67,main,,0,0,0,,Ooshu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.69,main,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.35,main,,0,0,0,,Take him to safety...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.17,main,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.18,main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.17,main,,0,0,0,,You're going to leave the forest, Shaga-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.89,main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I couldn't decline such request easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.68,main,,0,0,0,,It's because you involved yourself with the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.11,main,,0,0,0,,You even used one of your rings; such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.38,main,,0,0,0,,It's not everyday such things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.53,main,,0,0,0,,Yatagarasu-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:06.94,main,,0,0,0,,Shaga. You may not be aware why you're interested in human matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.74,main,,0,0,0,,it is from wishing to find another way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.99,main,,0,0,0,,Wishing another way of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.06,main,,0,0,0,,Help those in need and perform virtuous deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.34,main,,0,0,0,,Eventually you'll be granted the benevolence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:32.40,main,,0,0,0,,Shaga. Although Mother insisted, you need not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.55,main,,0,0,0,,I will walk with my own to feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.35,main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet he won't last long if he's attacked again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:43.11,main,,0,0,0,,I see, I bet my monster form is frightening too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.44,main,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.76,main,,0,0,0,,I want to become independent as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:52.45,main,,0,0,0,,so I can become a proud man like my deceased Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.70,main,,0,0,0,,Shall I teach you to use a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.95,main,,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.51,main,,0,0,0,,Please, please teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.62,main,,0,0,0,,Does that means I'm coming too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.28,main,,0,0,0,,Hmph, I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:25.40,main,,0,0,0,,Because of your secret medicine, my crotch has...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.28,main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Kiyomori-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.66,main,,0,0,0,,It appears that your proud member is too much for Yorihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:37.47,main,,0,0,0,,Let it be, she has a certain charm that her elder sister lacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.88,main,,0,0,0,,Oh really, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.24,main,,0,0,0,,Yorihime, lick the shaft underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:43.74,main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:49.50,main,,0,0,0,,That's it, now stick your tongue into the tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.13,main,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.90,main,,0,0,0,,Alright. Next, lift your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.98,main,,0,0,0,,Kiyomori-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.24,main,,0,0,0,,You really are beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.16,main,,0,0,0,,And, you're all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.51,main,,0,0,0,,Kiyomori-sama is serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.68,main,,0,0,0,,You do your best too, Yorihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.79,main,,0,0,0,,How cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.11,main,,0,0,0,,Very cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.78,main,,0,0,0,,I'll let you drink it soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.06,main,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:58.58,main,,0,0,0,,You surely jest! I'm still good to go because of the medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.13,main,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.00,main,,0,0,0,,then please go here next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.54,main,,0,0,0,,Please give your affection to Toyohime, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:06.92,main,,0,0,0,,Nee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.68,main,,0,0,0,,What an obscene display! It's twitching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:16.00,main,,0,0,0,,This is... It's just nervous about your proud member, Kiyomori-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:20.73,main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to thoroughly punish your obscene hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:23.99,main,,0,0,0,,the mouth that'll instantly eat me up as soon as I put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.59,main,,0,0,0,,This-! It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.25,main,,0,0,0,,It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.13,main,,0,0,0,,How rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.22,main,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I hear you scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:49.56,main,,0,0,0,,There's no argument, you're definitely cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.22,main,,0,0,0,,Kiyomori-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:03.24,main,,0,0,0,,It's reaching to places where it mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:06.22,main,,0,0,0,,I see, so this is your precious spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.36,main,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.29,main,,0,0,0,,No... No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:19.02,main,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm cumming! I'm gonna...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.16,main,,0,0,0,,So good-!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.67,main,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.60,main,,0,0,0,,Toyohime-sama, where shall I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.70,main,,0,0,0,,It's fine, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.72,main,,0,0,0,,What is this, it's frightening...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.82,main,,0,0,0,,It's truly terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.20,main,,0,0,0,,Leave it up to us, Kiyomori-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.53,main,,0,0,0,,We'll grant you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.12,main,,0,0,0,,Nee-sama, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:09.94,main,,0,0,0,,That's right, there's no need to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.82,main,,0,0,0,,I'm the supreme ruler of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:16.88,main,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be frightened; this place is paradise on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.56,main,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:52.18,main,,0,0,0,,What? You're going to cross that mountain right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.89,main,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:57.58,main,,0,0,0,,Rumor says horrifying monsters lurk in those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.86,main,,0,0,0,,Some of us have never returned either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:06.76,main,,0,0,0,,There's even been blood-soaked clothing and a horse caucus that came down the river recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:12.01,main,,0,0,0,,There must be some horrendous monster upstream, big enough to eat whole horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.38,main,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, Ushiwaka. Let us detour around the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:21.38,main,,0,0,0,,I... I want to become a strong warrior. Is it okay for me to run away from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:24.18,main,,0,0,0,,Ushiwaka, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.90,main,,0,0,0,,If there's a terrifying monster that's troubling people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.45,main,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:32.28,main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, won't I be defeating it then...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.16,main,,0,0,0,,Young man, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:36.84,main,,0,0,0,,If it's true, then please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.57,main,,0,0,0,,The monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:43.65,main,,0,0,0,,He's worried about the woman living in the mountains all by herself.
